#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/protocols.rst:61 8b5572a3199e457bb0290a86370b35f1
msgid "ESP32 自身并不支持 lora 通信，芯片没有集成 lora 协议栈与对应的射频部分。ESP32 可以外接集成 lora 协议的芯⽚，作为主控 MCU连接 lora 芯片，可以实现 Wi-Fi 与 lora 设备的通信。"
msgstr "ESP32 itself does not support LoRa communication, because the chip does not integrate the LoRa protocol stack or the corresponding RF part. ESP32 can be connected externally to a chip that integrates the LoRa protocol. As the main control MCU connected to the LoRa chip, ESP32 can implement communication between Wi-Fi and LoRa devices."

