#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/protocols.rst:113 2e6bc0fe6ada4a408a5fa534b08d568b
msgid "SNTP 协议中使用 UTC 与 GMT 的方法为何获取不到目标时区的时间？"
msgstr "Why cannot the time of the target time zone be obtained when using UTC and GMT in the SNTP protocol?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/protocols.rst:115 e53797e124bd482da27d32e446999798
msgid "TZ = UTC-8 被解释为 POSIX 时区，在 POSIX 时区格式中，这 3 个字母是时区的缩写(任意)，数字是时区落后于 UTC 的小时数。 UTC-8 表示时区,缩写为 “ UTC” ，比实际 UTC 晚 -8 小时, 即 UTC + 8 小时。故 UTC+8 是比 UTC 落后 8 小时, 就出现了 UTC+8 比正确的北京时间相差 16 小时的情况。"
msgstr "TZ = UTC-8 is interpreted as a POSIX time zone. In POSIX time zone format, these three letters are the time zone abbreviation (arbitrary), and the number indicates the number of hours the time zone lags behind UTC. UTC-8 means the time zone abbreviation is “UTC”, and it lags behind actual UTC by -8 hours, that is, UTC + 8 hours. Therefore, UTC+8 means 8 hours behind UTC, resulting in a 16-hour difference from the correct Beijing time."

