msgstr "Does ESP-12F support controlling devices through Tencent Cloud?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/protocols.rst:187 f0a3beb389f24ddabbb592e96e0a71ab
msgid "支持，烧录腾讯云固件（获取链接： `点击  <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-at/zh_CN/release-v2.2.0.0_esp8266/Customized_AT_Commands_and_Firmware/Tencent_Cloud_IoT_AT/index.html>`__）或者自主开发均可实现； 腾讯云固件使用串口引脚为：TXD=GPIO15, RXD=GPIO13"
msgstr "Yes. It can be implemented by flashing Tencent Cloud firmware (`click here <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-at/zh_CN/release-v2.2.0.0_esp8266/Customized_AT_Commands_and_Firmware/Tencent_Cloud_IoT_AT/index.html>`__) or by independent development. The serial pins used by the Tencent Cloud firmware are: TXD=GPIO15, RXD=GPIO13."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/protocols.rst:191 c007b38fc8744de5ac191e8ba6a0c8e8
msgid "请问ESP-01S模组是否可以烧录直连腾讯云固件？"
msgstr "Can the ESP-01S module be flashed with firmware for direct connection to Tencent Cloud?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/protocols.rst:192 29fd7a0583d24a24934409f32dcd6f7b
msgid "不支持，flash容量不足。入网腾讯云可以用AT MQTT固件通过配置MQTT指令的方式实现连接腾讯云的功能。"
msgstr "No. The flash capacity is insufficient. To connect to Tencent Cloud, you can use AT MQTT firmware and configure MQTT commands to connect to Tencent Cloud."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/protocols.rst:195 af309847c8bd4671853181fcf357c007
msgid "请问ESP-12F模组经常发生服务器掉线问题要怎么办？"
msgstr "What should I do if the ESP-12F module often disconnects from the server?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/protocols.rst:196 9b88c123ac6e40da9f190a7d3bfe879e
msgid "先排查是wifi离线了还是与服务器连接断开了，若是wifi断开了，排查模组与路由之间连接是否给踢掉。或者路有信号太弱。若是与服务器断开了，是否被服务器踢掉了，还是网络不稳定。"
msgstr "First check whether Wi-Fi is disconnected or the connection to the server is disconnected. If Wi-Fi is disconnected, check whether the connection between the module and the router has been kicked off, or whether the router signal is too weak. If the server connection is disconnected, check whether it was kicked off by the server or whether the network is unstable."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/protocols.rst:199 99442b9a7c7040bf910a6f71ef747fba
msgid "ESP-07的MQTT协议版本是多少"
msgstr "What MQTT protocol version does ESP-07 use?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/protocols.rst:200 2d5bf5bc02af40918ecc5fc023748a1a
msgid "MQTT协议版本为3.1.1"
msgstr "The MQTT protocol version is 3.1.1."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/protocols.rst:203 4a643060bdb048f59e4b08e2dc68fa78
msgid "ESP-01S模块配置作为TCP server模式使用如何保存配置"
msgstr "How to save the configuration when the ESP-01S module is configured as a TCP server?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/protocols.rst:204 9c78d4a12dcd44a0b4022b7114e0cf48
msgid "AT固件目前不支持该功能，需要对模块固件做二次开发实现"
msgstr "The AT firmware currently does not support this function. Secondary development of the module firmware is required."

#~ msgid ":link_to_translation:`en:[English]`"
